@startuml
title Viaverse Worker Profile — State Diagram

[*] --> NOT_CREATED
NOT_CREATED --> DRAFT : start onboarding
DRAFT --> PENDING_VERIFICATION : submit verification
DRAFT --> ACTIVE : verification not required
PENDING_VERIFICATION --> ACTIVE : approved
PENDING_VERIFICATION --> VERIFICATION_REJECTED : rejected
VERIFICATION_REJECTED --> DRAFT : fix and resubmit
ACTIVE --> PAUSED : worker pauses
PAUSED --> ACTIVE : resume
ACTIVE --> SUSPENDED : risk/admin
SUSPENDED --> ACTIVE : appeal/fix
DRAFT --> DELETED : delete
ACTIVE --> DELETED : account deletion
DELETED --> [*]

note bottom
PAUSED is worker-controlled and reversible.
SUSPENDED is policy/admin-controlled and blocks opportunities until resolved.
end note
@enduml
